name: アイリ - Airi Queen's Blade / クイーンズブレイド
description:
N°33 Release, アイリ - Airi From Queen's Blade - クイーンズブレイド.

You can now request a Character's LORA. CLICK HERE

Put everything in Filter for seeing all images!

Click on Show more for Weight & Trigger recommendation, Also click on About This Version at Right Corner for more Info.

Character's Request.

About this Lora:

  • Lora trained on 94+ Images that i sorted manually, at the max quality possible (Orginal Art 4K + Official Art 4K), Were used in the datasets) SFW+NFSW.

  • Can do Official Default Skin precisely.

  • Flexibility is Good.

  • NAI Used, Work with Any Lora & Majority of Anime Model's.

  • Work's Perfectly at Weight 1.

  • Work's greatly with Detail Tweaker Lora. (I Recommend to use it)

For Prompts & Weight:

About Trigger Words & Prompts: AiriV4 (For Trigger) & for prompts just refer to examples images & you can put any prompts you want.

Weight recommended: 0.6-1. - Best Result 0.7-1.

Leave a Review & Share you're image in comments if you appreciate this Work :).

modelVersions.description:
I pruned Eyes color & Hair, since Airi have 2 version with Blue & Green Eyes, if you want More Blue eyes type: ((Blue Eyes)), For Green Eyes: ((Green Eyes)) prompt.

For default skin, put 0.7-1 Weight, See examples Image for this. ( I Also recommends to put ((Twintails, Long hair)) promtps if they don't appear.

For Flexibility for like clothes that don't exist put 0.7 - 0.9 Weight, See my Examples images for this.

Also if you don't want something to appear, put it in Negative Promp
